('91418','31484','5','Hotel with 24 rooms for refurbishment in the first sea line '),
('91419','31485','5','This hotel is right on a beach promenade of a very popular tourist resort. \r\nThe plot has approx 250m² and the constructed area approx. 1.000m² and 200m² basement for storage, staff toilets and changing rooms. 24 room are distributed over 4 stores. A nice chill out lounge cold be created on the roof terrace with spectacular sea views.\r\nThe hotel has a hotel license. The owner started in 2013 to rehabilitate and is created ready to approximately 75%. Supply lines for electricity and water are already laid. Also, the air conditioning is pré installed. The windows (aluminum double glazing) are installed. It still lacks doors, cabinets, sinks, shower stalls, floor tiles and furniture. An elderly elevator will have to replaced. Very interesting object for someone who would like to acquire a with bed and breakfast boutique hotel. \r\nThe price has been reduced and is no longer negotiable.\r\n'),
